  "detailed_description": "Lanterns is a co-operative platformer where two players must work together to solve a gauntlet of unique puzzles. Players control a red and blue character that are able to shine a ray of light, of like colour. Objects in the world react in many ways when illuminated by these mystical lights, however timing, precision and a lot of communication will be required to conquer each trial.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay as Red or Blue and navigate through levels, or lead your teammate to temporary inevitable doom. Unlock different characters and along the way, and discover secret areas.",
  "about_the_game": "Lanterns is a co-operative platformer where two players must work together to solve a gauntlet of unique puzzles. Players control a red and blue character that are able to shine a ray of light, of like colour. Objects in the world react in many ways when illuminated by these mystical lights, however timing, precision and a lot of communication will be required to conquer each trial.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay as Red or Blue and navigate through levels, or lead your teammate to temporary inevitable doom. Unlock different characters and along the way, and discover secret areas.",
